---
import Site from "../layouts/Site.astro";
---

<Site title="Studio Ke">
	<section aria-labelledby="journey-heading">
		<h2 id="journey-heading" class="section-heading">My sewing journey</h2>
		<div class="prose">
			<p>
				[Tell the story of how you got into sewing — what drew you in, what your first project was, what kept you going.]
			</p>
			<p>
				[A second paragraph — share a piece you're proud of, or a moment where something clicked. Talk about the kinds of garments you love making and the people you love making them for.]
			</p>
			<p>
				[A third paragraph — what you're working on right now, and where you hope Studio Ke is in a year or two. This is the page that turns curious visitors into customers, so let your voice come through.]
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Site>
